Class XmlReporter

java.lang.Object
  generator.XmlReporter

public class XmlReporter
extends java.lang.Object

Java class to be launched by manually on the server,
that generate weekly reports at PowerPoint format.
It uses property file ppt.properties to generate the report with custom parameters.
